                "markerContent": "2",
                "title": "Fragmented standards",
                "content": "50+ useful but incompatible frameworks (SBTi, ACT, CDP, TPI…). Each measures one angle. None gives the full picture."
              },
              {
                "markerContent": "3",
                "title": "Unfair comparison",
                "content": "Without sectoral adjustment, comparing the climate efforts of an energy company and a software publisher makes no sense."
              }
