                "title": "Pillar A — Reduce",
                "subtitle": "Decarbonize operations and value chain",
                "content": "Scopes 1-2-3 emissions, transition plans, governance, supplier/client engagement, policy influence. Applies most to: steel manufacturers, energy producers, heavy industry."
              },
              {
                "markerIcon": "zap",
                "markerTheme": "brand",
                "title": "Pillar B — Amplify",
                "subtitle": "Deploy solutions enabling others to reduce",
                "content": "Green revenues, avoided emissions, low-carbon technologies. This is the CCF's most differentiating pillar. Applies most to: renewable energy providers, battery manufacturers, cleantech."
              },
              {
                "markerIcon": "dollar-sign",
                "markerTheme": "success",
                "title": "Pillar C — Finance",
                "subtitle": "Direct capital to climate projects beyond your value chain",
                "content": "Carbon credits, climate philanthropy, dedicated funds, green bonds, secondary impact investments. Applies most to: financial institutions, high-margin companies."
